  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0002",
      "text": " 179",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0003",
      "text": " Figure 5 – Image pairs",
      "bbox": [
        263.82,
        262.97,
        372.16,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0004",
      "text": "PRLI, if required, is performed after N_Port Login is successful and prior to other FC-4 transfers.  Ex-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.97,
        539.97,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0005",
      "text": "amples of use of the Process Login function may include image initialization, image re-configuration,",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.97,
        540.01,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0006",
      "text": "or when the Nx_Port receives an indication that the image pair no longer exists.  PRLI allows each",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.97,
        539.97,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0007",
      "text": "image behind an Nx_Port to separately manage its resources.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        369.87,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0008",
      "text": "PRLI may be used to establish an operating environment between any of the following combinations",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        539.95,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0009",
      "text": "of Nx_Port facilities:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        184.27,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0010",
      "text": "a) two Nx_Ports",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        382.96,
        181.8,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0011",
      "text": "b) one Nx_Port and one Nx_Port image",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        406.96,
        285.69,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0012",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        430.96,
        114.35,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0013",
      "text": "two Nx_Port images",
      "bbox": [
        122.37,
        430.96,
        211.82,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0014",
      "text": "An image pair may be established or modified with a PRLI request and LS_ACC reply Sequence set.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        539.93,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0015",
      "text": "Failure to establish a particular image pair does not affect existing image pairs or the ability to estab-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        540.07,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0016",
      "text": "lish other image pair.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        188.81,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0017",
      "text": "PRLI may also be used to exchange Service Parameters without establishing image pairs.  However,",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        540.05,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0018",
      "text": "if an image pair is currently established, a subsequent PRLI request targeted to the same Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        539.95,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0019",
      "text": "pair shall identify an image pair in order to modify Service Parameter settings for that image pair.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        522.59,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0020",
      "text": "If a PRLI request is received for an established image pair, the established image pair is unaffected",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        539.99,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0021",
      "text": "and the PRLI request is processed normally.  This allows the exchange of Service Parameters for a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        540.0,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0022",
      "text": "FC-4 not specified when the original image pair was established.  PRLO shall be used to remove an",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        539.96,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0023",
      "text": "established image pair.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        198.7,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0024",
      "text": "It shall be the responsibility of the ULPs to ensure that all active operations over an image pair have",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        539.93,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0025",
      "text": "been properly terminated prior to issuing a PRLI request that replaces Service Parameters.  If the re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        539.98,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0026",
      "text": "placement of Service Parameters affects any active operations, all open Sequences and Exchanges",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        634.96,
        540.04,
        646.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0027",
      "text": "shall be terminated by invoking Abort Sequence (ABTS). Whether or not the replacement of Service",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        539.99,
        658.13
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0028",
      "text": "Parameters affects an active operation shall be specified for each Service Parameter by the associ-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        540.09,
        670.13
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p198_s0029",
      "text": "ated FC-4.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        671.02,
        143.17,
        682.13
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
